University Core Curriculum. Once you are a student at UNT you will be able to access your personalized Interactive Degree audit through www.MyDegreeAudit.unt.edu.  Degree Plans for 2016-2017 Composition Composition Instrumental Performance Performance - Orchestral Instruments Performance - Multiple Woodwinds Jazz Studies Jazz Studies (instrumental, arranging or vocal emphasis) Keyboard Performance Performance - Organ Church Music Performance - Organ Performance - Harpsichord Performance - Piano Pedagogy Performance - Piano  Music (Bachelor of Arts program) BA Music BA Music - Music History and Literature Music Education (General, Choral and Instrumental Music with Teacher Certification) Music Education Music Theory Music Theory Vocal Performance Performance - Voice Music as a minor   Degree Plans for Previous Academic Years 2015-2016 Composition Composition Instrumental Performance Performance - Orchestral Instruments Performance - Multiple Woodwinds Jazz Studies Jazz Studies (instrumental, arranging or vocal emphasis) Keyboard Performance Performance - Organ Church Music Performance - Organ Performance - Harpsichord Performance - Piano Pedagogy Performance - Piano  Music (Bachelor of Arts program) BA Music BA Music - Music History and Literature Music Education (General, Choral and Instrumental Music with Teacher Certification) Music Education Music Theory Music Theory Vocal Performance Performance - Voice Music as a minor 2013-2014 BA Music BA Music - Music History and Literature 2012-2013 Composition Jazz Performance Jazz Arranging Jazz Voice  Instrumental Studies Multiple Wood Winds Music Ed - Elementary Band Music Ed - Band  Music Ed - Orchestra  Music Ed - Voice Music Ed – Keyboard or Guitar  Music Theory  Organ Church Music  Organ Performance Harpsichord Performance Piano Pedagogy  Piano Performance  Voice Performance Music as a minor 2012 BA Music BA Music - Music History and Literature 2011 BA Music Composition Jazz Performance Jazz Arranging Jazz Voice  In